    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "I know this is an old issue but it seems like the 'init' event call is still `void` so we don't really know if it's been initialised yet.\r\n\r\nHas anyone found a workaround for this, aside from above? How come we don't have access to know if it's been initialised (or have I missed some documentation)?",
